## ğŸŒ± Beginner (Dasar)
> ğŸ¯ Fokus: syntax Pythonic dasar, sering dipakai di preprocessing & eksplorasi data.

âœ… **Materi Utama**
- ğŸ”¹ Built-in functions â†’ `len`, `sum`, `max`, `min`, `sorted`, `enumerate`, `any`, `all`, `zip`
- ğŸ”¹ String & list ops â†’ `join`, `split`, `strip`, slicing
- ğŸ”¹ Tuple unpacking â†’ `(X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test)`
- ğŸ”¹ List & dict comprehension sederhana
- ğŸ”¹ F-strings untuk logging hasil training
- ğŸ”¹ Loop Pythonic â†’ `for item in items` ketimbang index manual
- ğŸ”¹ `with` statement untuk file dataset

ğŸ“Œ **Contoh di ML**
```python
# filtering data
data = [1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8]
filtered = [x for x in data if x % 2 == 0]  
print(filtered)  # [2,4,6,8]

# zip feature dan label
features = [1,2,3]
labels = [0,1,0]
dataset = list(zip(features, labels))
print(dataset)  # [(1,0), (2,1), (3,0)]
```

