## ğŸš€ Advanced (Lanjutan)
> ğŸ¯ Fokus: optimasi pipeline, resource management, & clean code ala ML Engineer.

âœ… **Materi Utama**
- ğŸ”¹ Generators & `yield` â†’ batch data loading (hemat RAM)
- ğŸ”¹ Generator expressions `(x**2 for x in range(10))`
- ğŸ”¹ Itertools & functools (`chain`, `groupby`, `reduce`, `partial`)
- ğŸ”¹ Decorators â†’ logging training, caching
- ğŸ”¹ Context managers custom (`__enter__`, `__exit__`)
- ğŸ”¹ Dataclasses â†’ definisi config model
- ğŸ”¹ Type hints & annotations â†’ kolaborasi tim
- ğŸ”¹ Dunder methods â†’ bikin custom Dataset class (PyTorch style)
- ğŸ”¹ Pattern matching (Python 3.10+)
- ğŸ”¹ Async/await â†’ paralel data loading / API model
- ğŸ”¹ PEP8 & clean code best practices

ğŸ“Œ **Contoh di ML**
```python
# Generator untuk batch data
def batch_generator(data, batch_size):
    for i in range(0, len(data), batch_size):
        yield data[i:i+batch_size]

data = list(range(100))
for batch in batch_generator(data, 10):
    print(batch)  # tiap iterasi keluar batch size 10
```

